{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-jsx","path":"/how-to-check-for-empty-space-tab-or-newline-in-python","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>The built-in string method <code class=\"language-text\">isspace()</code> checks if there are only whitespace characters in the string, otherwise it will return False.\nThe best use case of this method is to check if the string contains characters as:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>'\\n' - new line</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">mystring <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\n'</span>\nmystring<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isspace<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token boolean\">True</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>' ' - whitespace</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">mystring <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">' '</span>\nmystring<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isspace<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token boolean\">True</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>'\\t' - tab</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">mystring <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\t'</span>\nmystring<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isspace<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token boolean\">True</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>'\\r' - carriage return</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">mystring <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\r'</span>\nmystring<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isspace<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token boolean\">True</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>'\\f' - form feed</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">mystring <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\f'</span>\nmystring<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isspace<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token boolean\">True</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Or combination:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">mystring <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">' \\t'</span>\nanotherstring <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\n\\t'</span>\nmystring<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isspace<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nanotherstring<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isspace<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token boolean\">True</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token boolean\">True</span></code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Note that <code class=\"language-text\">isspace()</code> will not return True for '', so always check with <code class=\"language-text\">not mystring or mystring.isspace()</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>","timeToRead":1,"excerpt":"The built-in string method  checks if there are only whitespace characters in the string, otherwise it will return False.\nThe best use case…","frontmatter":{"title":"How to check for empty space, tab or newline in Python","date":"2020-06-01 23:22:13 +0200","categories":["python"],"tags":["python","strings"],"description":null,"keywords":"python, strings","author":"Zoran Pandovski","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAPCAYAAADkmO9VAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAZ0lEQVQ4y2Mw5v//n5qYYdRAODbiw60JnxwDPg2GvAhsBKP58BuK04UgzRai//9biUNoM2EIbSJAhgtBWJ/r/3831f//Yx3//4+w/v8/yvb//2i7//+tJSCWDbyXqRopNDFwNOsRjQHOdKSa6R2eoAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==","width":540,"height":400,"src":"/static/18b0edfdfa96fadbadd7955f1202cbd7/819a5/python.png","srcSet":"/static/18b0edfdfa96fadbadd7955f1202cbd7/819a5/python.png 1x"}}}},"fields":{"slug":"/how-to-check-for-empty-space-tab-or-newline-in-python","date":"2020-06-01T21:22:13.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/how-to-check-for-empty-space-tab-or-newline-in-python","nexttitle":"What is Big O notation?","nextslug":"/what-is-big-o-notation","prevtitle":"ClickHouse Code 516. DB::Exception","prevslug":"/clickhouse-code-516-dbexception","tagList":["abstraction","OOP","Class","java","collection","API","Map","HashMap","LinkedHashMap","TreeMap","Python","cli","args","argparse","javascript","es6","beginner","codenewbie","Primary_key","implementation","Composite_key","language-support","localization","internationalization","linux","file permissions","Project Euler","Algortithms","SQL","database","commands","GO","Datatypes","Variables","Constants","HTML5","Web development","tricks","NumpPy","array","python","NLP","libraries","text processing","go","golang